>>>>>>> ## Diabetes UK’s policy on different types of diabetes research
>>>>>>> Diabetes UK carries out a range of different types of diabetes
research, to help people living with the condition.
>>>>>>> Diabetes UK is a member of the Association of Medical Research
Charities (AMRC) and adheres to their guidelines on the use of animals in
research, which can be downloaded from the AMRC website.
>>>>>>> The Position statements & reports section contains Diabetes UK's
official views on a variety of topics. You can also find our position
statements on animal and stem cell research below:
